{"tid":1779861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩大家唔好再反環保少女","createTime":"2019-12-12T03:06:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T03:49:15.000Z","uid":61099,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b9cf2de6521a01f7b7924a6ba0d23a28e788c8db","tid":1779861,"uid":61099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T03:06:39.000Z","msg":"比返d氣量同尊重 連登既內容叫做反映到部份香港人既質素 <br />\n<br />\n就算大家對環保少女既負面評價係理性同合理都好 都請各位忍一忍口 踩佢彈佢笑佢既內容國際好多媒體或者網站都已經做左 <br />\n所以請大家默默地接受 然後享受下國際間&quot;鄧&quot;為我地唔抵既言論<br />\n<br />\n再加上風雲人物當選到亦唔代表d乜野 直情唔應該有贏輸既觀念 <br />\n<br />\n最後再講多次<br />\n麻煩大家唔好再反環保少女"},{"pid":"603b709753fc1638d98f2f960c2287c8d0ef1057","tid":1779861,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T03:08:41.000Z","msg":"5demand~ how dare you!"},{"pid":"5340ac7f1db8433cf711292f4ae64779aa893b9b","tid":1779861,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T03:09:01.000Z","msg":"佢提倡環保，但係自己唔環保，好似d冷氣軍師成日叫手足be water，但係從來未上過前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df393738608fa4ed2430767e55577e25eaa80d11","tid":1779861,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5340ac7f1db8433cf711292f4ae64779aa893b9b","tid":1779861,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T03:09:01.000Z","msg":"佢提倡環保，但係自己唔環保，好似d冷氣軍師成日叫手足be water，但係從來未上過前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T03:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/Yhc1zqN.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"bf43b5cfb4645f2cce7930578f887374efbe1b09","tid":1779861,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T03:10:36.000Z","msg":"晒時間反佢不如諗點抗爭好過啦"},{"pid":"15f45efd5d00d227860171301119e684b4f058e5","tid":1779861,"uid":333694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T03:11:20.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"f91dde18751707b9e8cb88b32278846c647afde4","tid":